Requires [text editor][link:../reference/extension/editor] extension.

This would maps to the main text editor’s text selection range API that is created by the text editor extension:

~~~ .js
// `Panel.forms.TE.{$form_id}.{$textarea_name)`
Panel.forms.TE['form.m.page'].content;
~~~

From that, you can use the available API as described in [this documentation page](https://tovic.github.io/text-editor/text-editor/ui). Example:

~~~ .js
// Show a prompt modal
var editor = Panel.forms.TE['form.m.page'].content;
editor.ui.prompt('What is your name?', "", false, function(e, $, v) {
    $.insert('Your name is: ' + v);
});
~~~